HEADWORD: Lakh
<hw>Lakh</hw>
<pr>(l⟦aum⟧k)</pr> }</mhw>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Hind. <ets>lak</ets>,
<ets>l⟦amac⟧kh</ets>, <ets>l⟦amac⟧ksh</ets>, Skr. <ets>laksha</ets> a
mark, sign, lakh.]</ety> <def>One hundred thousand; also, a vaguely
great number; <as>as, a <ex>lac</ex> of rupees</as>.</def>
<altsp>[Written also <asp>lack</asp>.]</altsp> <mark>[East
Indies]</mark>⟦br⟧
